OL,5, Scientists say they may have found the 
OL,6, best strategy for calming upset babies.
OL,8,FForget controlled crying or rocking in 
OL,9,Fa crib.                                
OL,11,FAccording to a small but novel study,  
OL,12,Fwhich asked parents to try a range of  
OL,13,Fmethods, walking for five minutes while
OL,14,Fcarrying the infant and then sitting   
OL,15,Fwith them in your arms for another five
OL,16,Fbefore putting them down to sleep in   
OL,17,Ftheir cot, is the most successful.     
OL,19,FThe findings appear in the journal     
OL,20,FCurrent Biology.                       
